## Accepting the Edit

Once you're satisfied with the proposed change,
[`accept()`](`EditValidation.accept`) executes the revised plan and returns a `Validate`
object, ready to interrogate:

::: {#8488f586 .cell execution_count=7}
``` {.python .cell-code}
plan = edited.accept()          # a Validate (not yet interrogated)
plan.interrogate()              # run it
```

